Texts.Chs: 干得漂亮。我想是时候进行下一步了。
Texts.Eng: Great work. I think it's time to move on.

Texts.Chs: 从零到最终建成一个完备的实验室的过程中，甲醇都在扮演着一个重要的角色。你可以把^orange;原木^reset;萃取而得到甲醇。
Texts.Eng: Methanol will be useful in the production of a number of goods and eventually get you on track to a masterful laboratory. ^orange;You'll find it via wood extraction^reset;.
